email_content:
Dear Sarah,

I hope youre doing well! Heres a concise look at the most recent admissions cycle:

 Applications continued their steady rise, resulting in our largest applicant pool to date.
 Selectivity also increased, with a small percentage of applicants receiving offers of admission.
 The incoming class is academically strong; their average standardized test scores place them near the top of national benchmarks.
 Students will be joining us from more than 60 countries, making this one of the most internationally diverse cohorts weve welcomed.
 Interest in interdisciplinary and sustainability-focused programs saw particularly notable growth.

Were excited about the energy and perspectives this group will bring to campus later this year. If youd like additional details or are interested in helping us welcome the newest members of the Pride, just let me know!

Warm regards,

John
Alumni Relations Coordinator
Prestige University
